rules.description: Fn + B              Open Visual Studio Code
Fn + JKIL           Arrow Keys (with Cmd as Shift)
Fn + H;             Move cursor by word, left & right (with Cmd as Shift)
Fn + UO             Move->line Start, End (with Cmd as Shift)
Fn + /              Delete line full (with CMD + Backspace)
Fn + F              Open Finder with open ~/Downloads
